    <string name="about_explanation">\
ReminderMail is an app that will let you quickly send e-mail to a pre-defined address.
This is useful to quickly send reminders to yourself, or to an online ToDo-list application (such as &lt;a href=\"http://www.nirvanahq.com\">NirvanaHQ&lt;/a> or &lt;a href=\"http://www.toodledo.com\">Toodledo&lt;/a>).
    </string>
    <string name="about_shortcut">Move the ReminderMail icon to your home screen for easy access, or share pages via \"@ ReminderMail\".</string>
    <string name="about_limitations">Note that ReminderMail only supports one e-mail address.</string>
